@startuml
' שליטה במצב ניטור רשת '

actor Network
participant SysAdmin
participant Toggle as MonitorToggle

== Continuous Capture ==
SysAdmin -> MonitorToggle : request toggle
activate MonitorToggle
alt Request == Enable
    MonitorToggle -> Network : Start Monitoring
    MonitorToggle --> SysAdmin: Monitoring Enabled
else Request == Disable
    MonitorToggle -> Network : Stop Monitoring
    MonitorToggle --> SysAdmin: Monitoring Disabled
end
deactivate MonitorToggle

@enduml
